@startuml
title ATM Control

[*] --> Idle

state Idle
state "Waiting for PIN" as WaitingForPIN
state "Validating PIN" as ValidatingPIN
state "Waiting for Customer Choice" as WaitingForChoice
state "Processing Transaction" as ProcessingTransaction {
  state "Processing Transfer" as ProcessingTransfer
  state "Processing Query" as ProcessingQuery
  state "Processing Withdrawal" as ProcessingWithdrawal
}
state Ejecting
state Printing
state Dispensing
state Confiscating

Idle : entry / Display Welcome
Idle --> WaitingForPIN : Card Inserted / Get PIN

WaitingForPIN --> ValidatingPIN : PIN Entered / Validate PIN
ValidatingPIN --> WaitingForPIN : Invalid PIN / Invalid PIN Prompt
ValidatingPIN --> Confiscating : Third Invalid PIN, Card Stolen, Card Expired / Confiscate
ValidatingPIN --> WaitingForChoice : Valid PIN / Display Menu

WaitingForPIN --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject
ValidatingPIN --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject
WaitingForChoice --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject

WaitingForChoice --> ProcessingTransaction : Select Transaction
ProcessingTransaction --> Ejecting : Rejected / Eject, Display Apology
ProcessingTransfer --> Printing : Transfer Approved / Print Receipt, Update Status
ProcessingQuery --> Printing : Query Approved / Print Receipt, Update Status
ProcessingWithdrawal --> Dispensing : Withdrawal Approved / Dispense Cash, Update Status

ProcessingTransaction --> ProcessingTransfer : Transfer / Process Transfer
ProcessingTransaction --> ProcessingQuery : Query / Process Query
ProcessingTransaction --> ProcessingWithdrawal : Withdrawal / Process Withdrawal

ProcessingTransfer --> Ejecting : Rejected / Eject, Display Apology
ProcessingQuery --> Ejecting : Rejected / Eject, Display Apology
ProcessingWithdrawal --> Ejecting : Rejected / Eject, Display Apology

Dispensing --> Ejecting : Dispensing Complete / Eject
Printing --> Ejecting : Printing Complete / Eject
ProcessingQuery --> Ejecting : Query Complete / Eject
ProcessingTransfer --> Ejecting : Transfer Complete / Eject
ProcessingWithdrawal --> Ejecting : Withdrawal Complete / Eject

Confiscating --> [*] : Card Confiscated

@enduml
